data.text:
Dear European Parliament,

Under the right of access to documents in the EU treaties, as developed in Regulation 1049/2001, I am requesting documents which contain the following information:

CVs of the MEPs who served diring the 7th legislature and the list of party group coordinators for each committee.

Thank you very much for your attention

Yours faithfully,

Eugenio

Dear Mr Frisetti Carpani,

With respect to your application dated 22 April 2016 concerning the CVs

of the MEPs who served during the 7th legislature and the list of party

group coordinators, please find enclosed the requested documents.

Kind regards,
